title: Avant-The_VIII-(2015)
description:
Veteran R&B singer/songwriter Avant released his eighth studio album, The VIII, via MO-B Entertainment/Caroline. Led by the single, "Special", the thirteen-song album features production by Travis Sayles and Bob Robinson (Tim & Bob). Support him and buy his new album, out NOW!
